│ IndVarSimplify assumes LCSSA form with valid SE analysis. The key difference is that %indvar2 in the source has  │
│ value 1 on the first iteration, 0 on the second, and 1 on the third, while in the target it's incorrectly        │
│ assumed to always be 1 (true).\n\n2. Analyzing `opt`'s Log: The opt log shows that LCSSA is applied first (with  │
